                            <comment id="18029756" author="garydgregory" created="Tue, 14 Oct 2025 12:01:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hello &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=hylkevds&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;hylkevds&quot;&gt;hylkevds&lt;/a&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

