                            <comment id="18029761" author="hylkevds" created="Tue, 14 Oct 2025 12:14:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It does not seem to be fixed in commons-lang3-3.19.1-20250929.203706-6&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Which commit was supposed to fix this issue?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="18029762" author="hylkevds" created="Tue, 14 Oct 2025 12:15:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;My PR has two commits, the first one adds a test that demonstrates the issue.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;That test fails on the master branch in GitHub.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="18029765" author="garydgregory" created="Tue, 14 Oct 2025 12:27:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hello &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=hylkevds&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;hylkevds&quot;&gt;hylkevds&lt;/a&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You need to test with version &lt;tt&gt;3.20.0-SNAPSHOT&lt;/tt&gt;. Notice the fixed version in this ticket says &quot;3.20.0&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The GitHub CI had a random failure on Windows with Java 25.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
